# WordPress Uploads Directory
#
# This directory is mounted as a Persistent Volume Claim (PVC) in Kubernetes.
# Files uploaded through WordPress will be stored here.
#
# In production:
#   - Mounted from PVC for persistent storage
#   - Survives pod restarts and redeployments
#
# In development:
#   - Mounted from local directory
#   - Changes persist locally
#
# NOTE: This directory should NOT contain vendored files.
# Only user-uploaded content should be stored here.
